    • ExploreMapSizeDesire

      public ExploreMapSizeDesire(Belief belief, String teamMate, String teamMateActionName, String supervisor, String direction, int guideOffset)
      Instantiates a new ExploreMapSizeDesire.
      Parameters:
      belief - the belief of the agent
      teamMate - the name of the team mate which helps to explore the map size
      teamMateActionName - the full name of the team mate (provided by the simulation server) which helps to explore the map size
      supervisor - the name of the supervisor of the group
      direction - the direction the agent should start to explore
      guideOffset - the number of cells the agent is off the planned exploration line when receiving the Desire.
